message.body: So you like cashews?
I do. Do you like beetle juice?
The movie I mean :)
Haha eh its OK. It was the first thing that popped into my head when I was making a user name
Yeah coming up with usernames can be annoying, reminds me if aol screen names from the 90s
True story. Mine were always dumb. So you out if school?
Of*
Yeah, I graduated in 2003. Or did you mean out for the summer?
What about you? Are you a student?
Nope. I graduated in 2012. So a bit younger than you. Why'd you sign up for the study?
Where did you go?
I work at LDC
O very cool! Do you like it? I went to UVA
Yeah, it's interesting work
What kind of work do you do?
Its the linguistic data consortium right? I am in IT services. Basically I configure and install software systems
Yeah. Did you go to school for computer science ?
Yea pretty much. Systems engineering and computer science. Wanted to make sure I could get a job haha
That seems to be one of the only fields where finding a good job is easier
Are you still in Virginia?
Haha yea seriously. Sorry for not responding, lots of meetings today
I'm based in VA but work in NY
That's a long commute!
I'm headed to the gym but I'll try to txt layer
*later
Well I only make the trip twice a week. Life of a traveling consultant, living in hotels and sleeping on trains
Good for you! I'm gonna try to go after work
